106
00:11:49.584 --> 00:11:53.713
A small moment when the prince is unprotected.

107
00:11:55.048 --> 00:11:57.259
The Great Thaedus. Don't misunderstand.

108
00:11:57.342 --> 00:12:00.512
I would gladly kill Thragg
for a million reasons.

109
00:12:00.595 --> 00:12:02.556
but doesn't that still leave more than 40 -

110
00:12:02.639 --> 00:12:05.225
increasingly angry
