122
00:12:45.307 --> 00:12:51.188
But it is worth all the sacrifices
to show the Viltrum Empire...

123
00:12:51.271 --> 00:12:54.024
absolutely and definitively.

124
00:12:54.107 --> 00:12:58.278
that even their
their strong empire is not...

125
00:12:58.361 --> 00:13:04.326
UNWINNABLE

126
