167
00:15:18.001 --> 00:15:20.754
In fact.
if I really had to choose.

168
00:15:20.837 --> 00:15:22.797
Paul's spaghetti.

169
00:15:22.881 --> 00:15:26.176
He's my mother's boyfriend.
He even makes his own meatballs.

170
00:15:27.844 --> 00:15:30.472
Brain bowl from Galactic Grill.

171
00:15:31.723 --> 00:15:33.808
