200
00:17:25.252 --> 00:17:27.255
Thragg is stronger.

201
00:17:27.881 --> 00:17:30.133
Don't drift apart.

202
00:17:30.216 --> 00:17:33.428
So don't try to fight
against him alone. Oliver.

203
00:17:33.511 --> 00:17:34.804
I'm not trying to.

204
00:17:34.888 --> 00:17:36.639
We stay together.

205
00:17:36.723 --> 00:17:38.433
That's how we will win this.

206
00:17:39.392 --> 00:17:41.102
If something happens.

207
00:17:41.936 --> 00:17:43.438
remember that I...

208
00:17:48.234 --> 00:17:49.319
We know.

209
00:17:59.037 --> 00:18:01.539
I am really annoyed.
if I do not survive.

210
00:18:04.000 --> 00:18:06.044
Is everyone ready?

211
00:18:07.253 --> 00:18:08.546
Follow the plan.

212
00:18:08.630 --> 00:18:10.673
Slip past the sensors...

213
00:18:10.757 --> 00:18:13.802
and explore the planet
as quickly as possible.

214
00:18:14.427 --> 00:18:18.056
You have the information of the Prince
the most likely whereabouts of the prince.

215
00:18:18.473 --> 00:18:21.726
