has any meaning.

218
00:18:44.499 --> 00:18:46.084
What are you waiting for?

219
00:18:49.295 --> 00:18:51.422
Go save the galaxy already.

220
00:19:01.558 --> 00:19:02.559
Are those...

221
00:19:02.642 --> 00:19:03.643
They are.

222
00:19:04.018 --> 00:19:08.231
The assassination of Emperor Argall
and the Great Purge...

223
00:19:08.314 --> 00:19:10.233
