266
00:25:49.757 --> 00:25:52.009
Just to talk to an old friend.

267
00:25:52.802 --> 00:25:54.679
Since when are we on speaking terms?

268
00:25:55.680 --> 00:25:57.348
We have always talked.

269
00:25:58.140 --> 00:26:00.601
Some just chose not to listen.

270
00:26:01.978 --> 00:26:03.104
So talk.

271
00:26:06.649 --> 00:26:08.109
Go home. Nolan.

272
00:26:09.151 --> 00:26:11.988
Return home and all will be forgiven.

273
00:26:14.407 --> 00:26:15.950
We don't have a home.

274
00:26:17.243 --> 00:26:19.370
This place is a tomb.

275
00:26:19.453 --> 00:26:21.664
Viltrum is not a tomb.

276
00:26:28.170 --> 00:26:29.505
It is part of us.

277
00:26:32.466 --> 00:26:34.844
We will restore it to the way it was.

278
00:26:34.927 --> 00:26:39.015
as we also restore our people
to their rightful place in the galaxy.

279
00:26:40.099 --> 00:26:42.935
There are barely 40 of us left.

280
00:26:44.478 --> 00:26:46.063
Forty people from Viltrum.

281
00:26:46.981 --> 00:26:49.400
who know you
better than you do.

282
00:26:49.483 --> 00:26:51.694
They have fought alongside you...

283
00:26:51.777 --> 00:26:55.281
and have suffered just like you.

284
00:26:56.157 --> 00:26:58.159
You are no longer my family.

285
00:26:59.410 --> 00:27:03.164
Unlike the man who almost
killed us to extinction. did he?

286
00:27:03.998 --> 00:27:07.418
I know that Thaedus created a plague virus.

287
00:27:07.501 --> 00:27:09.879
Yet you fight alongside him.

288
00:27:10.880 --> 00:27:14.175
He committed genocide
against his own people.

289
00:27:14.258 --> 00:27:17.595
To prevent us from doing the same to others.

290
00:27:17.678 --> 00:27:21.599
You know we only did what was necessary
to maintain order.

291
00:27:21.682 --> 00:27:23.893
Such as. for example
you attacked my boys.

292
00:27:25.019 --> 00:27:28.439
We tested your son.
as we have all been tested.

293
00:27:29.315 --> 00:27:31.525
Do you think Thaedus is
as favourable to them.

294
00:27:31.609 --> 00:27:33.235
if he wins the war?

295
00:27:40.242 --> 00:27:43.287
I see you're not
as naive as I feared.

296
00:28:06.727 --> 00:28:09.146
Ridiculous creatures.

297
00:28:09.230 --> 00:28:11.524
Embarrassing at best.

298
00:28:11.607 --> 00:28:15.611
That's how you think about all species
except yours. Lucan.

299
00:28:16.112 --> 00:28:18.572
You will soon be taught a lesson.

300
00:28:58.112 --> 00:28:59.029
Hang in there.

301
00:28:59.113 --> 00:29:01.115
An external object is repaired.

302
00:29:05.870 --> 00:29:07.955
Thank you.

303
00:29:08.038 --> 00:29:10.124
You're welcome. Keep beating them up.

304
00:29:17.256 --> 00:29:21.051
This hall echoes with
once a thousand voices.

305
00:29:22.511 --> 00:29:27.475
Everyone was united by the knowledge that.
that the universe belonged to Viltrum.

306
00:29:28.517 --> 00:29:30.436
Argall showed it to us.

307
00:29:31.020 --> 00:29:33.272
He showed us our true power.

308
00:29:34.899 --> 00:29:35.900
Thaedus...

309
00:29:36.984 --> 00:29:38.694
Thaedus was a coward.

310
00:29:39.695 --> 00:29:41.655
You know that. don't you?

311
00:29:41.739 --> 00:29:43.365
It doesn't change anything.

312
00:29:43.908 --> 00:29:48.329
When you fight for him.
you fight for your own destruction.

313
00:29:48.412 --> 00:29:50.831
For the destruction of your family.

314
00:29:50.915 --> 00:29:53.083
I will not let him harm my family.

315
00:29:54.418 --> 00:29:56.128
You have already done so.

316
00:29:57.713 --> 00:29:59.423
This is over. Thragg.

317
00:29:59.840 --> 00:30:03.511
The whole galaxy is against us
as one front.

318
00:30:03.594 --> 00:30:06.347
but it doesn't have to
end with our extinction.

319
00:30:06.430 --> 00:30:09.558
Agree to the terms and I'll put an end to this.

320
00:30:09.642 --> 00:30:11.810
whatever Thaedus wants.

321
00:30:12.478 --> 00:30:15.898
Would our Emperor ever agree to the terms?

322
00:30:16.607 --> 00:30:18.526
Look around you. Thragg.

323
00:30:19.068 --> 00:30:21.111
We lost.

324
00:30:21.195 --> 00:30:23.864
Can't you see why all this was ruined?

325
00:30:23.948 --> 00:30:25.866
This is our home.

326
00:30:26.784 --> 00:30:28.536
We will rebuild it.

327
00:30:31.288 --> 00:30:32.331
No.

328
00:30:33.499 --> 00:30:34.708
You don't build.

329
00:30:38.671 --> 00:30:42.591
The death of any Viltrum resident
leaves an empty hole in my heart.

330
00:31:17.835 --> 00:31:20.588
Hey. dickhead! Wormhole was asking for you.

331
00:31:21.839 --> 00:31:23.757
It's looking for the biggest bastard in the universe.

332
00:31:26.260 --> 00:31:28.137
You are not one of us.

333
00:31:34.560 --> 00:31:35.519
Oliver!

334
00:31:39.732 --> 00:31:40.566
No!

335
00:31:45.613 --> 00:31:47.531
That child was unworthy.

336
00:31:47.615 --> 00:31:49.617
He wasn't your real brother.

337
00:31:50.284 --> 00:31:52.077
I killed the Conqueror.

338
00:31:52.161 --> 00:31:53.621
I'll kill you too.

339
00:31:58.792 --> 00:32:00.085
Show me.

340
00:32:16.560 --> 00:32:18.479
I am not impressed.

341
00:32:48.884 --> 00:32:49.843
Zoe!

342
00:32:50.719 --> 00:32:51.553
Quickly.

343
00:32:55.182 --> 00:32:57.017
Out of ammunition.

344
00:32:57.101 --> 00:32:58.894
Damn! I ran out of arrows.

345
00:33:17.371 --> 00:33:21.083
Kill me if you can.
and die if you can't.

346
00:33:22.084 --> 00:33:24.461
so I can find a better opponent.

347
00:33:24.545 --> 00:33:25.379
Animal!

348
00:33:44.732 --> 00:33:45.733
Finally!

349
00:33:46.567 --> 00:33:47.651
No.

350
00:33:58.704 --> 00:34:00.748
Everyone with me. Now.

351
00:34:21.018 --> 00:34:23.103
Forget him. I need you.

352
00:34:23.187 --> 00:34:24.980
What do we do?

353
00:34:25.105 --> 00:34:26.899
Spaceman. take point!

354
00:34:37.034 --> 00:34:38.452
No! Stay with me!

355
00:34:44.792 --> 00:34:45.793
No.

356
00:34:46.627 --> 00:34:48.128
We can't!

357
00:34:48.212 --> 00:34:50.172
Mark. trust me.

358
00:34:52.132 --> 00:34:53.926
Spacedriver. now!

359
00:34:57.221 --> 00:34:58.222
No.

360
00:34:59.389 --> 00:35:00.933
No!

361
00:35:29.962 --> 00:35:31.213
Stay close!

362
00:35:32.422 --> 00:35:33.757
Stay together!

363
00:40:08.365 --> 00:40:09.199
Zoe!

364
00:40:33.473 --> 00:40:36.685
It was the only way to show them the truth.

365
00:40:38.979 --> 00:40:40.021
I know.

366
00:40:42.315 --> 00:40:44.192
Oliver. Where is Oliver?

367
00:41:05.547 --> 00:41:07.090
Viltrumites!

368
00:41:07.757 --> 00:41:11.511
Your world is destroyed!

369
00:41:12.512 --> 00:41:16.725
Surrender is your only option.

370
00:41:16.808 --> 00:41:19.728
No!

371
00:41:23.940 --> 00:41:26.568
I choose death!

372
00:41:36.870 --> 00:41:38.663
Emperor Argall.

373
00:41:39.539 --> 00:41:41.750
your death has been avenged.

374
00:41:48.381 --> 00:41:51.551
It's your turn next. all of you.

375
00:41:57.224 --> 00:41:58.141
Thaedus.

376
00:41:58.767 --> 00:41:59.768
Oh my God.

377
00:42:00.518 --> 00:42:02.729
Allen. find Oliver.

378
00:42:04.397 --> 00:42:05.357
Allen!

379
00:42:05.899 --> 00:42:07.776
Yeah. okay.

380
00:42:13.657 --> 00:42:15.700
I offered you forgiveness!

381
00:42:16.201 --> 00:42:21.039
I offered you an honourable death!

382
00:42:23.625 --> 00:42:29.172
Instead. you destroyed everything!

383
00:42:48.858 --> 00:42:51.069
I killed Thaedus too quickly.

384
00:42:51.152 --> 00:42:54.447
I won't make the same mistake with you!

385
00:42:59.327 --> 00:43:00.912
Okay. I understand.

386
00:43:00.996 --> 00:43:04.499
You are a bit surprised
and angry about what you just said.

387
00:43:07.085 --> 00:43:09.254
Spacedriver!

388
00:43:51.588 --> 00:43:52.797
Allen!

389
00:43:56.343 --> 00:43:57.177
Zoe!

390
00:43:57.260 --> 00:43:59.220
Don't worry. I took care of him.

391
00:44:02.807 --> 00:44:03.850
We have to go!

392
00:44:04.642 --> 00:44:06.811
We can't leave Mark and Nolan.

393
00:44:06.895 --> 00:44:08.063
And where is Oliver?

394
00:44:08.146 --> 00:44:09.522
We cannot help them.

395
00:44:47.894 --> 00:44:50.105
You could have been a Viltrumite.

396
00:44:50.730 --> 00:44:52.690
but you decided not to...

397
00:44:55.568 --> 00:44:56.528
How to -

398
00:44:57.195 --> 00:44:58.196
we beat him?

399
00:44:59.072 --> 00:44:59.989
Mark...

400
00:45:22.137 --> 00:45:23.054
Dad!

401
00:45:26.391 --> 00:45:27.767
What a waste.

402
00:46:19.569 --> 00:46:22.322
Grand Duke. kill him!

403
00:46:23.156 --> 00:46:25.658
They destroyed our homes!

404
00:46:25.742 --> 00:46:26.826
Shut up!

405
00:46:32.957 --> 00:46:34.459
There are too few of us -

406
00:46:34.542 --> 00:46:35.710
already now.

407
00:46:45.762 --> 00:46:49.641
What are your orders. Grand Duke?

408
00:48:18.021 --> 00:48:19.105
Hello.

409
00:48:19.188 --> 00:48:20.481
Hey. buddy. Mark?

410
00:48:21.316 --> 00:48:22.442
Are you awake?

411
00:48:23.651 --> 00:48:24.902
You are.

412
00:48:24.986 --> 00:48:26.946
Well. well. well. Welcome back.

413
00:48:29.198 --> 00:48:30.241
Allen.

414
00:48:30.617 --> 00:48:31.492
For how long?

415
00:48:32.035 --> 00:48:33.077
A couple of weeks.

416
00:48:33.161 --> 00:48:35.121
For a while it looked bad.

417
00:48:35.204 --> 00:48:38.291
You certainly know how to test
the nerves of an unopian.

418
00:48:43.546 --> 00:48:45.798
Where is Oliver? Where is my father?

419
00:48:58.227 --> 00:48:59.187
Dad!

420
00:49:06.486 --> 00:49:07.779
You are alive.

421
00:49:07.862 --> 00:49:09.238
I woke up yesterday.

422
00:49:10.073 --> 00:49:11.074
Oliver...

423
00:49:11.949 --> 00:49:13.242
He'll be fine.

424
00:49:14.369 --> 00:49:16.037
He just needs time to recover.

425
00:49:16.788 --> 00:49:18.915
What happened to Thragg and the others?

426
00:49:19.040 --> 00:49:21.751
What is the last thing you remember?

427
00:49:22.752 --> 00:49:24.045
I was in Thragg's grip.

428
00:49:24.587 --> 00:49:26.839
I thought you were dead.

429
00:49:27.632 --> 00:49:29.008
Why did he spare us?

430
00:49:30.218 --> 00:49:31.511
Good question.

431
00:49:32.136 --> 00:49:33.930
but we have more important things.

432
00:49:34.389 --> 00:49:35.223
What?

433
00:49:35.807 --> 00:49:36.933
Where are they?

434
00:49:37.016 --> 00:49:38.893
That's it.

435
00:49:41.354 --> 00:49:42.730
As you know...

436
00:49:46.109 --> 00:49:48.403
As you know. Thaedus is dead.

437
00:49:50.780 --> 00:49:53.533
The Council asked someone to take the lead.

438
00:49:53.616 --> 00:49:56.703
until a successor can be appointed.

439
00:49:56.786 --> 00:49:59.038
And believe it or not.

440
00:49:59.122 --> 00:50:00.832
the job fell to me.

441
00:50:00.915 --> 00:50:03.418
There is essentially one small problem for me.

442
00:50:03.501 --> 00:50:05.336
The remaining Viltrumites.

443
00:50:05.420 --> 00:50:06.587
Yep.

444
00:50:06.671 --> 00:50:08.089
General Telia?

445
00:50:08.589 --> 00:50:13.761
We explore space sector by sector.
but they have simply disappeared.

446
00:50:13.845 --> 00:50:15.805
It makes everyone nervous.

447
00:50:16.639 --> 00:50:19.183
Hiding is a good sign. isn't it?

448
00:50:19.267 --> 00:50:22.520
The people of Viltrum do not usually want to...

449
00:50:24.147 --> 00:50:25.314
Mark. what is it?

450
00:50:28.693 --> 00:50:30.027
They have gone to Earth.

451
00:51:28.294 --> 00:51:30.296
Subtitles by Tero Vaaja

452
00:51:30.379 --> 00:51:32.381
Creative inspector
Pirkka Valkama
